{"tid":820287,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FBI局長：美反間諜首要針對中國","createTime":"2018-09-15T10:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T11:20:21.000Z","uid":141151,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf83f2616b1927491dbffd7784412edb7c93cf1","tid":820287,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"FBI局長：美反間諜首要針對中國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2161774/FBI%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%8D%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E9%A6%96%E8%A6%81%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2161774%2FFBI%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%2595%25B7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25A6%2581%25E9%2587%259D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B&d=bWgaZwBvmeazD3cCoRUlqRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=38d9acfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2161774/FBI%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7%EF%BC%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%8D%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E9%A6%96%E8%A6%81%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n中美關係因貿易戰而變得緊張之際，美國聯邦調查局（FBI）局長克里斯托弗雷（Christopher Wray）表示，沒有任何國家比中國對美國構成的威脅更大，中國是美國反間諜工作的首要對象。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，FBI在全國的56個地方辦公室，幾乎全部都有涉及中國商業間諜活動的案件，並指中國的間諜活動以不同的形式展開，包括網絡攻擊、盜取知識產權，又涉及通過不同的人群對外宣傳，包括政府派出的間諜，非傳統類的教授、商人、研究生，以及像華為、中興這樣的電訊企業。<br />\n<br />\n而為防範中國的科技間諜，FBI等美國情報機關近期據報已展開調查，重點排查「千人計劃」（即引進海外高層次人才的國家戰略）學者，部分已遭逮捕、驅逐出境或拒發簽證。"},{"pid":"d7d2c4bbd3bd0f2a2d0db646c4524372f95a0244","tid":820287,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T11:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309a6a82efa93476ee9785d998b63959c21f5cca","tid":820287,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f2dfda743f08dc835d85160e8eb01676024591","tid":820287,"uid"